✅ How to Run the Project
Open terminal in the LoginApp folder.

Run this to install Flask if not installed:

bash:
pip install flask

Initialize the database:
python init_db.py

Start the Flask app:
bash
python app.py

Open browser and visit:
👉 http://127.0.0.1:5000/

